# The coach agent reads secrets from the repo-root .env (one secrets file for
# the whole project), so you normally DON'T create a file here. This example
# only documents what the agent needs.
#
# Already present in the root .env (used by the iOS app + viewer):
#   LIVEKIT_URL
#   LIVEKIT_API_KEY
#   LIVEKIT_API_SECRET
#
# You must ADD this one to the root .env before running the agent:
#   GOOGLE_API_KEY=...        # https://aistudio.google.com/apikey  (Gemini API key)
#
# Optional overrides (have sensible defaults in coach_agent.py):
#   COACH_MODEL=gemini-3.1-flash-live-preview
#   COACH_VOICE=Puck
#   COACH_SPEAKING_FPS=1.0
#   COACH_SILENT_FPS=0.3
